<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Login Method Mismatch</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f23 0%, #1a1a2e 50%, #16213e 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(120, 119, 198, 0.3) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(255, 119, 198, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 40% 40%, rgba(120, 200, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .container {
      background: rgba(17, 25, 40, 0.8);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 48px;
      max-width: 520px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow:
        0 32px 64px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05),
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
      position: relative;
    }

    .container::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2), transparent);
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(40px) scale(0.96);
      }

      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
      }
    }

    .icon {
      width: 88px;
      height: 88px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b, #ffa726, #ff5722);
      border-radius: 22px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      box-shadow:
        0 20px 40px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.2),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      position: relative;
    }

    .icon::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: -2px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b, #ffa726, #ff5722);
      border-radius: 24px;
      z-index: -1;
      opacity: 0.3;
      filter: blur(8px);
    }

    @keyframes float {

      0%,
      100% {
        transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg);
      }

      33% {
        transform: translateY(-8px) rotate(1deg);
      }

      66% {
        transform: translateY(4px) rotate(-1deg);
      }
    }

    .icon svg {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      fill: white;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3));
    }

    h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #e2e8f0);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .message {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
      padding: 24px;
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.5);
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.1);
      border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      position: relative;
    }

    .message::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3), transparent);
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-direction: column;
      margin-top: 32px;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 16px 28px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      border: none;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .btn::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: -100%;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), transparent);
      transition: left 0.5s;
    }

    .btn:hover::before {
      left: 100%;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #1d4ed8, #1e40af);
      color: white;
      box-shadow:
        0 8px 24px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow:
        0 16px 32px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #1d4ed8, #1e40af);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.8);
      color: #e2e8f0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.9);
      border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.3);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .help-text {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #64748b;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
        padding: 36px 24px;
        margin: 16px;
        border-radius: 20px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .icon {
        width: 76px;
        height: 76px;
        border-radius: 18px;
      }

      .icon svg {
        width: 38px;
        height: 38px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="icon">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path d="M11 15h2v2h-2zm0-8h2v6h-2zm.99-5C6.47 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.47 10 9.99 10C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12S17.52 2 11.99 2zM12 20c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8z" />
      </svg>
    </div>

    <h1>Whoops! Account Mismatch</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">Different login method detected</div>

    <div class="message">
      We found an existing account associated with your Google account, but it was created using a different login method (email & password).

      To access your account, please use your original email and password instead of Google Sign-In.
    </div>

    <div class="actions">
      <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>/login" class="btn btn-primary">
        Sign in with Email & Password
      </a>


    </div>

    <div class="help-text">
      Please use your email and password to access your existing account.
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    // Add interactive behavior
    document.querySelectorAll('.btn').forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('mouseenter', function() {
        this.style.transform = 'translateY(-2px)';
      });

      btn.addEventListener('mouseleave', function() {
        this.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>

</html>